{"type": "article", "id": 24178, "title": "意面化身为女孩发型，这个包装出自俄罗斯设计师之手", "description": "设计师们在食品包装领域大有可为啊。", "date": "2016-03-21T12:35:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2841, "name": "食品包装"}, {"id": 25177, "name": "意面"}, {"id": 25178, "name": "创意包装"}, {"id": 373, "name": "俄罗斯"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 245, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702123951yE3aUkBsnHSYePI6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">逛超市的时候，如果在货架上看到下图中女孩的发型，你是否会停下脚步、多看几眼？只要吸引到了人们的注意力，设计师 Nikita Konkin 的目的就达到啦。<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2016/03/19/pasta-packaging-turns-product-into-hairstyles/\">这位俄罗斯设计师的新作是意面的包装，</a>不同形态的意面构成了女孩的造型，着实很吸引人啊！</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123941nqXvZFtocRi76Bs1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">包装上的女孩们发型各异，有卷发也有黑长直</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021239412VnEU0MiSCq8eLJD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.18875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">来看看近照吧</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021239427hUi2EISRG3uFm5f.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.18875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">这一款是小卷发</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123943ufDSTcOJMK7xWHhV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.18875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">这一款则是黑长直啦</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.behance.net/nikitos/wip\">Nikita Konkin</a> 是一位俄罗斯设计师，他 Behance 页面只有 400 多位关注者，但他的很多作品都挺有意思。我们打算介绍一些比较有个性的作品：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021239433CyNJr6VGmOZ2TiK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.315\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">他在 Goodlak 展上创作的小雕塑</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021239440CAxomL1DysRXQaO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66225166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">他为 Wamiles SMM 做的平面广告</p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123944B1AChMRjL6Xl58pZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">为 Wamiles SMM 做的平面广告</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123945E52KOHoNP6BarwfI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66225166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">再来一张相关品牌的平面广告</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123945N1yGD90q2vVdZH86.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Nikita Konkin 为可口可乐制作的平面广告</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123946aQgCVbJG2yRA8Dwo.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">可口可乐广告画</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123946XVEZf1OaljeyPuJW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Nikita Konkin 设计的信用卡</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123947tnON9dew28ixrc4B.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123947kuQ0i1HoB7xJFfMc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">这是信用卡的手绘草图啦</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">想更深入地了解这位俄罗斯设计师，可以登录他的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/nikitos/wip\">Behance 页面</a>。</p>\n<p class=\"\">介绍完这位俄罗斯设计师，我们再来看看其他有趣的意面包装吧：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123948Up4KFzlIxerRijfD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.15333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">这款糖果色的包装出自瑞典女设计师 Julia Grafström 之手</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123948iRLh10oUeCZkQEuX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.745\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123949MxQbWEm6coD9n1JI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">这是另外一款</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123949krx3adKWlUJyps72.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.305\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">在这款设计里，意面也是发型担当哦</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123949SapEQN1WxJqui9s5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.208\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123950tqNXG3wFPHJ4CQf5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25105485\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">动物包装的也很可爱</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2016/03/19/pasta-packaging-turns-product-into-hairstyles/\">contemporist</a></p>\n\n"}